Me: &quot;Whats up?&quot;<br>
Begger: &quot;I just died.&quot;<br>
Me: &quot;Okay. And?&quot;<br>
Begger: &quot;I need to get my corpse before it rots.&quot;<br>
Me: &quot;You have more than ample time to take the boat.&quot;<br>
Begger: &quot;Plz dude.&quot;<br>
Me: &quot;Listen, I just came from a very bad wipe out in Chardok and my corpse is right dab slap infront of the Overking as I ran like hell to save the clerics. I need to get my own corpse from a worse position.&quot;<br>
Begger: &quot;This will only take a second.&quot;<br>
Me: &quot;Sure, with your ungodly fast CPU it might only take me a second. But I gotta med up, take you to IC, kill whatever is at the ring for you without getting more, then leaving. I figure you could suck up to 10 minutes of time.&quot;<br>
Me: &quot;Plus theres a risk factor, mana factor. Can you pay me?&quot;<br>
Begger: &quot;No. Plz d00d&quot;<br>
Me: &quot;Nope, sorry.&quot;<br>
Begger: &quot;I guess Mr. All High and Mighty Taxi is too good to port the rest of us non-TPers around. Fine then, see if I help you ever&quot;<br>
