But changing the subject, how do you handle TP requests, when you ask for them, on your twinks? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukeiote.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keiote</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/17/01 5:00:46 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.graffe.com/darkmoon/keiote_sasnic_ani_3.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Do I play the taxi?</span><hr size=1> Keiote: /guildsay &quot;Hey Graffe you busy?&quot;<br>
